#!/usr/local/projects/routing/help/html_filter.pl
<h2 align=center>Help for the "Staff" search menu</h2>
You can reach this menu by clicking on the 'Staff' button
at the footer of this application.
<p>The Staff search menu allows you to search through all the
staff you have access to, and select which one to view.
<p>
The header for the search table shows the description of each of the columns.
If you click on the column header, you can enter a value and only show
staff with the specified value in that field.
<p>
Values in the search output are clickable:
<ul>
<li>Clicking on a <a href="record_Staff.cgi">staff</a> name will view information about
    that staff member.
<li>Clicking the <a href="record_Distributor.cgi">distributor</a> will show you information about that distributor.
<li>Clicking the <a href="field_Staff_Email.cgi">e-mail</a> address will bring up your mailer to allow you to
    send e-mail to that staff member.
<li>Clicking the <a href="field_Staff_Phone.cgi">phone number</a> will bring up your phone application to call
    that staff member (if available).
<li>Clicking on a <a href="field_Staff_Notify.cgi">notify</a> address (which will look like an e-mail address)
    will allow you to send e-mail to that persons e-mail or text them as
    they view more convenient.
</ul>

